  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201409/8c5f67773a21414e831dcb3b22660e30.png\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong>一语道破英语语法（上）<br />\n\t</strong>时间：5月27日（星期二） 20:00 - 21:00</span><br />\n\t<span style=\"color: #000;\">主讲老师：Vicki老师（</span><a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/u/26072512/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">点击关注老师的沪江部落&gt;&gt;&gt;</a><span style=\"color: #000;\">）</span><br />\n\t<span style=\"color: #000;\">公开课地点：English Activity Room（</span><a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/zt/cctalk/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">点击下载CCTalk&gt;&gt;&gt;</a><span style=\"color: #000;\">）</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #b22222;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">讲师简介： </span><br />\n\t</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Vicki<br />\n\t</span></strong>美籍台湾人。从事英语相关教学20年，培训学员人次近30万。旅居美国11年，深知英语的文化背景，语言结构以及中式英语的问题关键。培训课程涵盖学前语音语感训练，少儿英语，新概念英语1-4册，SAT,TOEFL,IELTS，GRE,GMAT,AP US History,AP Microeconomics,AP Macroeconomics,国际贸易，跨文化交流，日常英语对话，英语正音以及职场英语等项目。最擅长化繁为简，深入浅出的系统教学。上课风格独特，幽默风趣，是广大学生心目中的英语启蒙师。<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">（</span></span><a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/u/26072512/\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" target=\"_blank\">点击进入老师部落&gt;&gt;&gt;</a><span style=\"color: #000;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">）</span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #b22222;\"><strong>视频回顾：</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #b22222;\"><strong>课堂内容提要：</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>一、What's English</strong><br />\n\t1.Tense<br />\n\t2.Preposition<br />\n\t3.Clause</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>二、Tense</strong><br />\n\t1.Time<br />\n\t-Past,Present,Future,Past Future</p>\n<p>\n\t2.State<br />\n\t-Continuous,Perfect,Perfect-Continuous,Simple</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>三、Preposition</strong><br />\n\t-A gust of wind blows her hair up.<br />\n\t-A gust of wind blows her hair off.</p>\n<p>\n\t-in,on,at,over,for<br />\n\t-from,to,with,of</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>四、Clause</strong><br />\n\t-Clause contain &quot;Subject&quot; and &quot;Verb&quot; just like a simple statement does;however,clause can not be used alone without a main statement.<br />\n\t-The man who is wearing a skirt is my father.<br />\n\t-I don't understand what you said.<br />\n\t-Because the bus had a flat tire,I was late for class this morning.<br />\n\t-The bus had a flat tire,so Iwas late for class this morning.</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(178, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">想提前一周知道最精彩的公开课安排吗？那就来订阅沪江CCTalk电子报吧！<strong><a href=\"http://app.hujiang.com/mail/sub/72/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">电子报的订阅入口&gt;&gt;</a></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(178, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">沪江网校还为大家提供了其他的活动，欢迎大家预约：<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/app/event\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>最新活动预约</strong></a></span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201209/58f013100fe44857a846c5c5aef19325.gif\" style=\"width: 377px; height: 15px;\" /></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>请注意！参与本活动须使用沪江全新语音学习软件CCTalk，使用指南如下：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t1.<strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://bulo.hjenglish.com/n1/?source=eng2009\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">注册</span></a></strong>沪江网获得用户名（已是沪江用户的不必注册）；<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_gkkyd\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/fdac82641c98410a9fb1352dcdff5cd3.jpg\" /></a><br />\n\t2. 点击网址<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/zt/cctalk/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(7, 93, 179);\">http://class.hujiang.com/zt/cctalk/</span></a>下载CCtalk软件；<br />\n\t3. 软件安装结束后，输入沪江网的<b><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 100, 0);\">用户名</span></b>和<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 100, 0);\"><b>密码</b></span>登陆CCtalk；<br />\n\t4. 点击下图中用红圈标注的&ldquo;<strong><span s